metadata.name: O Fortuna #60
metadata.description:
"O Fortuna
Velut Luna
Statu variabilis

Semper crescis
Aut decrescis
Vita detestabilis
Nunc obdurat
Et tunc curat
Ludo mentis aciem
Egestatem
Potestatem
Dissolvit ut glaciem

Sors immanis
Et inanis
Rota tu volubilis"

As in the story of "Carmina Burana: O Fortuna", nothing is permanent, everything fluctuates, an emotional rollercoaster, sometimes up, sometimes down. The present situation should not define you, as your circumstances are ever-changing and uncertain. Remember that tomorrow is a new day and with it comes new opportunities for growth and improvement.

[S] to save a image file

made with p5.js , p5.js.noise
2023

metadata.name: Polyptych #105
metadata.description:
Polyptych is a 3D interactive installation inspired by generative plotter designs. It is also meant to be displayed as multiple prints taken from different angles, be it a diptych, triptych, tetraptych, or more.

For an example see: https://bgo.la/polyptych.png

Instructions:

- use the mouse to navigate around the piece (zoom, pan and drag)
- press 'c' to switch between multiple camera angles
- press 'space' to pause the animation
- press 'p' to take a screenshot in a custom resolution (always 1:1 ratio) of the current view. Note that taking a screenshot will only work when seeing the piece live (click 'Open live' on fxhash), not on the mint page because of the sandboxed iframe.

Berlin, December 2021
@bgola

metadata.description:
This painting is a combination of several artistic styles. We tried to create a special effect for each purchased work by creating various effects along with unique color palettes.
The buyer of the work will be the owner of an arrangement of ordinary pieces that is randomly created for him. Each buyer will have a color palette with a combination of effects.

*It should be noted that this work is not limited in terms of dimensions and the buyer can view and print the work in the largest dimensions.

Color Palette => 20
Grid => 25 - 100
Blend Mode => 4
Size => Small, Medium, Large
